invalid type: string "Org Chart: A visual map of the departments.\n\n\n\n\n\nKey Contacts: A \"cheat sheet\" of names for IT, HR, Finance, and their immediate manager.\n\n\n\n\n\nThe Buddy System: If applicable, introduce the concept of their assigned peer mentor.\n\n\n\n4. The First 30-60-90 Days\n\nShift the focus from \"learning\" to \"doing\" with a clear roadmap.\n\nPhase\n\nFocus\n\nity":290